      "note": "description",
      "abstract": "Establishes the Hawaii-Ireland Trade Commission within the Department of Business, Economic Development, and Tourism for administrative purposes.  Requires the Commission to submit annual reports to the Legislature and Governor.  Sunsets 6/30/2031.  (CD2)"
